{"type": "article", "id": 9043, "title": "编织玻璃", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-30T07:16:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235046aRVejgyG5wL1lZOh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tElisa Strozyk 是一位来自德国的设计师，毕业于伦敦中央圣马丁艺术与设计学院。最近，她推出了一款特殊的吊灯。吊灯由玻璃编织而成，编织是一种常见的技艺，而玻璃也是制作吊灯的常用材料。但编织玻璃去让人眼前一亮。这款设计获得了 2015 年德国设计奖。这是<a href=\"http://www.elisastrozyk.de/\" target=\"_blank\">作者的个人主页</a>，可以查看她的更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052350433gKzTSGhXl45weDO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66423358\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235043Iin3e0vsokJOupZl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66631908\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235044bWTtD1ZpIBnGzVei.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67291667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235045vhOnCdxQMSbKNZu6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66631908\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235045q5km9GQfKRLg0CsU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66840459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}